cc:Work.dc:title: Johnny's Cup of Coffee Coloured
cc:Work.dc:description: This is a remix of Johnny_Automatic's Cup of Coffee (from October 2006). I wanted to use his fantastic artwork for a small hobby project, but needed both black and white and semi-coloured versions. \n \nThanks to the generosity of Johnny in uploading his artwork in the first place, it took me no time at all to bring together what I needed. I'm not an artist, and so the colouring suits my needs but isn't particularly well done. However, the least I could do is upload it for anyone else that either wants to use it or improve upon my changes.
